txt.en: You have slain many slugs in the marshy muck of Agarnaith. You are not sure if this accomplished anything besides making Viznak a little happier.
'Swamp has lots of stuff I like to eat: mushrooms, rats, bugs. Know what else likes to eat those? Slugs! I hate slugs! They squishy and taste bad and they steal my food. We should kill some!'
Slimy blood-slugs can be found in the wilds of Agarnaith.\n\nYou should defeat slimy blood-slugs.
Viznak has asked you to cull some of the slugs from the Agarnaith swamp. Apparently, they are competition for the food he likes.
'Swamp has lots of stuff I like to eat: mushrooms, rats, bugs. Know what else likes to eat those? Slugs! I hate slugs! They squishy and taste bad and they steal my food. We should kill some!'
